metadata.name: Car Alpha #1
metadata.description: Car Alpha is the World's First Collection of Real Artwork of Futuristic and Antique Cars turned into NFTs. Created by a designer with a background of over 70 years of professional experience. The Artist is about 90 years old, and has been part of the design team of renowned companies in the automotive industry. (Site: https://caralpha.io / Twitter: https://twitter.com/caralpha_ / Discord: https://discord.gg/tmU2CMEZUx)
